fonts.html.title: fonts
fonts.html.contents: $typekit-font scss $typekit-font: ( 'name': 'freight-text-pro', 'stack': 'fantasy', 'source': 'https://typekit.com/fonts/freight-text', ); A font imported from typekit. call the specimen preview directly give a font-name and parenthetical list of variants on the first line suppy additional html head as a nested block Font Preview freight-text-pro (typekit) css font-family: 'freight-text-pro', fantasy; $google-font scss $google-font: ( 'name': 'Exo 2', 'source': 'https://fonts.google.com/specimen/Exo+2', 'stack': ('arial', 'monospace', 'fantasy'), ); A font imported from google fonts. call the specimen preview directly give a font-name and parenthetical list of variants on the first line suppy additional html head as a nested block Font Preview Exo 2 (google) css font-family: 'Exo 2', 'arial', monospace, fantasy; $local-font scss $local-font: ( 'name': 'rockingham', 'regular': ( 'path': 'rockingham/rockingham-regular-webfont', 'local': 'rockingham-regular-webfont', ), 'bold': 'rockingham/rockingham-bold-webfont', 'italic': 'rockingham/rockingham-italic-webfont', 'bold' 'italic': 'rockingham/rockingham-bolditalic-webfont', 'stack': 'fantasy', 'formats': 'woff2' 'woff' 'ttf', ); A locally-hosted font. call the specimen preview directly give a font-name on the first line optionally override variants with parenthetical list no additional html head add a font-path global config option, similar to sass path options Font Preview rockingham (local) css font-family: 'rockingham', fantasy; $data-font scss $data-font: ( 'name': 'latoregular', 'normal': ( 'woff': 'data:application/x-font-woff;charset=utf-8;base64,', ), 'stack': 'fantasy', ); An embedded data-uri font. call the specimen preview directly give a font-name on the first line optionally override variants with parenthetical list no additional html head add a font-path global config option, similar to sass path options Font Preview latoregular (data) css font-family: 'latoregular', fantasy;
